      "description": "A political candidate with a creepily soft voice and some unconventional views. Bastard Begetter: Claims to have had children by various women. Since he's not married, it's never adultery, so he doesn't think it's an issue. Character Tic: Raising and lowering his hands with index and middle fingers extended while he's speaking. Cloud Cuckoolander: He's definitely not all there. His policy proposals include \"America needs another big lake\" and killing every whale in the world for no reason he cares to explain. Cue Card... Pause: He reads almost everything he says off of index cards, which he's constantly stopping to turn over, leading to some awkward delivery.",
