      "description": "The titular character of the sketches. Making life-saving inventions out of household materials; getting in andoutof ultra sticky situations; the guy's a friggin genius. Eventuallygot his own movie. The Bus Came Back: For season 47 in 2022. That's a whopping 12 years. He also returned for a Season 51 episode in 2025. Comical Overreacting: Macgruber often overreacts to innocuous things other people do, like handing him an object. The innocuous thing is often something Macgruber had just asked them to do. Conspiracy Theorist: Played for laughs — when he returns in 2022 he's gone completely MAGA.\"Have you ever heard ofQAno-\" (kaboom)",
